(106, 1, '2024-02-13 16:48:34', '2024-02-13 15:48:34', '<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":48,\"width\":\"300px\",\"height\":\"300px\",\"scale\":\"cover\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"http://localhost/Esercizi_Epicode/ProgettoWP/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/f7a41ac65b4c7e67f8aa60c3d54a57b6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-48\" style=\"object-fit:cover;width:300px;height:300px\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":49,\"width\":\"300px\",\"height\":\"300px\",\"scale\":\"cover\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"http://localhost/Esercizi_Epicode/ProgettoWP/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/e646dbb1a06061a46b0432cc1ff9e7f6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-49\" style=\"object-fit:cover;width:300px;height:300px\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":50,\"width\":\"300px\",\"height\":\"300px\",\"scale\":\"cover\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"http://localhost/Esercizi_Epicode/ProgettoWP/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/1399c8b255c1e24947334ed5c60ac040.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-50\" style=\"object-fit:cover;width:300px;height:300px\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"20px\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:20px\"><em>Tra le dolci colline di una campagna rurale si estende un mare di viola e blu: il campo di lavanda. Un luogo incantato dove il profumo delicato si fonde con la vista di interminabili distese di fiori che ondeggiano leggeri al vento. Immersi in questa sinfonia di colori e profumi, ci si ritrova avvolti da un’atmosfera di tranquillità e serenità.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"20px\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:20px\"><em>Ogni passo è un invito a esplorare questa meraviglia della natura, ad assaporare la sua bellezza e a lasciarsi trasportare dalla sua magia.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"26px\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#c084d3\"}}},\"color\":{\"text\":\"#c084d3\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-text-color has-link-color\" style=\"color:#c084d3;font-size:26px\"><em>Benvenuti nel regno della lavanda, dove il tempo sembra fermarsi e i sensi si risvegliano in un’esperienza unica e indimenticabile.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"18px\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:18px\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":105,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/Esercizi_Epicode/ProgettoWP/home/f976a0a79a91d9f21b891e8f3f42f79f-2/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\",\"imageFill\":false} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-top\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/Esercizi_Epicode/ProgettoWP/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/f976a0a79a91d9f21b891e8f3f42f79f-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-105 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Contenuto…\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"16px\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">Immersi in un\'atmosfera di pura magia e tranquillità, i nostri campi di lavanda offrono un\'esperienza indimenticabile per tutti i sensi. Camminare tra le distese infinite di fiori viola, accarezzati dalla brezza leggera e avvolti dal profumo dolce e rilassante della lavanda, è un viaggio sensoriale che riempie il cuore di gioia e serenità.</span><p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(227, 227, 227); box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 1.25em; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">Ogni passo in questo paradiso terrestre è un\'opportunità per connettersi con la natura e ritrovare un senso di pace interiore. La vista dei campi di lavanda che si estendono all\'orizzonte, il suono delicato dei petali che si muovono al vento e il profumo avvolgente che riempie l\'aria creano un\'atmosfera di incanto e meraviglia.</p><p style=\"border: 0px solid rgb(227, 227, 227); box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-pan-x: ; --tw-pan-y: ; --tw-pinch-zoom: ; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-gradient-from-position: ; --tw-gradient-via-position: ; --tw-gradient-to-position: ; --tw-ordinal: ; --tw-slashed-zero: ; --tw-numeric-figure: ; --tw-numeric-spacing: ; --tw-numeric-fraction: ; --tw-ring-inset: ; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(69,89,164,.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; --tw-blur: ; --tw-brightness: ; --tw-contrast: ; --tw-grayscale: ; --tw-hue-rotate: ; --tw-invert: ; --tw-saturate: ; --tw-sepia: ; --tw-drop-shadow: ; --tw-backdrop-blur: ; --tw-backdrop-brightness: ; --tw-backdrop-contrast: ; --tw-backdrop-grayscale: ; --tw-backdrop-hue-rotate: ; --tw-backdrop-invert: ; --tw-backdrop-opacity: ; --tw-backdrop-saturate: ; --tw-backdrop-sepia: ; margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 1.25em; color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-s